OL,3,CDave Myers' wife thanks Hairy Bikers
OL,4,Cfans for 'massive wave of love'
OL,6,FThe wife of star Dave Myers has
OL,7,Fthanked his fans for the "massive wave
OL,8,Fof love, compassion and care that you
OL,9,Fhave shown towards me".
OL,11,FBarrow-born Myers, who was part of the
OL,12,Fmotorcycle-riding cooking duo with co-
OL,13,Fpresenter, Si King, following a battle
OL,14,Fwith cancer.
OL,16,FLiliana Orzac, who he met while
OL,17,Ffilming Hairy Bikers in Romania, was
OL,18,Fat his side along with King when the
OL,19,Fpresenter and TV chef died
OL,20,F"peacefully" at home.
