OL,3,CDave Myers' wife thanks Hairy Bikers
OL,4,Cfans for 'massive wave of love'
OL,6,FA message from her to the Instagram
OL,7,Fpage said: "I will never be able to
OL,8,Fthank you all enough for the massive
OL,9,Fwave of love, compassion and care that
OL,10,Fyou have shown towards me, Simon and
OL,11,Four families in these past days since
OL,12,FDave passed.
OL,14,F"I want you all to know that I have
OL,15,Fread every single message and comment
OL,16,Fthat you sent... your stories about
OL,17,FDave, your feelings you shared with me
OL,18,Fmean a lot and my heart is filled with
OL,19,Fgratitude and love.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@AOU
