OL,3,CDave Myers' wife thanks Hairy Bikers
OL,4,Cfans for 'massive wave of love'
OL,6,F"It amazes me how many hearts he
OL,7,Ftouched and how many people wanted to
OL,8,Fexpress their love for what Dave and
OL,9,FSi have created for nearly 20 years. I
OL,10,Fknow the Hairy Bikers have been part
OL,11,Fof your living rooms for such a long
OL,12,Ftime and I feel your loss as much as
OL,13,Fyou feel mine!
OL,15,F"My husband, David Myers was a larger
OL,16,Fthan life character and he did
OL,17,Feverything with passion, enthusiasm
OL,18,Fand generosity of spirit. His energy
OL,19,Fwas endless when it came to cooking
OL,20,Fand talking recipes, or biking and
OL,21,Ftalking bikes.
