OL,3,CDave Myers' wife thanks Hairy Bikers
OL,4,Cfans for 'massive wave of love'
OL,6,F"An amazing storyteller! And through
OL,7,Fhis stories and TV appearances he was
OL,8,Fconstantly inspiring and encouraging
OL,9,Fpeople to cook, travel, to live their
OL,10,Flife to the fullest.
OL,12,F"An exceptional husband, wonderful
OL,13,Fstepdad, loyal friend and in his own
OL,14,Fwords, a creator, never a follower.
OL,16,F"I feel I'm grieving with a whole
OL,17,Fnation... and this is something
OL,18,Fspecial. My wonderful Dave ` Lili
OL,19,FMyers."
