OL,6,FThe post was shared alongside a
OL,7,Fpicture of her and Myers.
OL,9,FShe co-owned his production company
OL,10,FSharpletter ` which had assets worth
OL,11,Fmore than #1.4 million, accounts filed
OL,12,Fon 31 January show.
OL,14,FMyers was a stepfather to her two
OL,15,Fchildren, Iza and Sergiu, from a
OL,16,Fprevious relationship.
OL,18,FKing and Myers' latest series, The
OL,19,FHairy Bikers Go West, is continuing to
OL,20,Fair on BBC Two.
